            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段下跌。英国富时100指数报10,042.64点，跌64.20点(0.64%)；德国DAX指数报22,754.79点，跌202.29点(0.88%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,811.35点，跌35.20点(0.45%)。 <br/> (WL)</span>\n</div>",
